name: Experiment Or Die #90
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. 8th letter in The Cool Alphabet this completes the Crypto phrase GM with G  Is For Gollum which everyone knows from Lord Of The Rings. I read The Hobbit as a kid but really fell in love with Tolkien around the time they started working on the movies. Gollum was such a tragic character. Couldn't forget about his PRECIOUS.
